>>> g = troposphere.guardduty.Detector('example', Enable=True)
>>> t.add_resource(g)
<troposphere.guardduty.Detector object at 0x1012701d0>
>>> print t.to_json()
{
    "Resources": {
        "example": {
            "Properties": {
                "Enable": "true"
            }
        }
    }
}
```

I will attempt to submit a pull request shortly unless this is already on someone's radar.

